steps.name: Given I am login on staging env
When I navigate to menu "Modules" without submenu
Then I should see Modules screen display
When I reset module "Cloudinary"
When I add module "Cloudinary"
When I expand Header "Production"
When I expand Header "Staging"
When I collapse Header "Staging"
When I expand Header "Development"
When I collapse Header "Development"
When I press Save button popover popup without wait
Then I should see inline error message of textbox has Header "Production" and label "Api Key" with message "Api Key is required"
Then I should see inline error message of textbox has Header "Production" and label "Api Secret" with message "Api Secret is required"
Then I should see inline error message of textbox has Header "Production" and label "Cloud Name" with message "Cloud Name is required"
Then I should see inline error message of textbox has Header "Production" and label "Enhance Image Tag" with message "Enhance Image Tag is required"
Then I should see inline error message of textbox has Header "Production" and label "Static Image Support" with message "Static Image Support is required"
When I input textbox has Header "Production" and label "Api Key" with value "jitera Api Key"
Then I should see eyed textbox with Header "Production" and label "Api Key" with value "jitera Api Key"
When I input textbox has Header "Production" and label "Api Secret" with value "jitera Api Secret"
When I input textbox has Header "Production" and label "Cloud Name" with value "jitera Cloud Name"
When I input textbox has Header "Production" and label "Enhance Image Tag" with value "jitera Enhance Image Tag"
When I input textbox has Header "Production" and label "Static Image Support" with value "jitera Static Image Support"
When I check checkbox has Header "Production" and label "Secure"
When I check checkbox on popover popup with label "add video utils"
When I press Save button popover popup
